 arch/arm/boot/dts/am335x-bone-panel-320x240.dtsi | 51 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 arch/arm/boot/dts/am335x-bone-panel-480x272.dtsi | 50 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 arch/arm/boot/dts/am335x-bone-panel-800x480.dtsi | 50 +++++++++++++++++++++++
